WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Meet Gemdex: memory your coding agents can share.

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.300
Save a playbook once, then recall it from any repo or machine.

00:00:07.300 --> 00:00:12.000
It searches chunks with Gemini and LanceDB,
but returns the whole memory.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.500
Local by default, remote when needed,

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:19.651
and always under your control.
